name: Simba messenger bag
description:
This bag is 100% recycled, and 100% of the profits go to Jobortunity in Arusha Tanzania. 

The bag itself is made from recycle cement bags, jute and recycled textiles. It's a one of a kind design, and you won't find anything like this on the high street. 

They are made locally in Arusha, so by purchasing the bag you'll benifit the local economy, as well as the students at Jobortunity!

There is a small pocket inside, and a fabric tie on the top to keep all your belongings secure. And the dimensions are 35cm x 35cm x 10cm... perfect for books, records and other things that need carrying around.

If you like the style, but don't like the design then message us. We've got loads of one of a kind styles that might take your fancy, so get in touch.
